parameters:
Welcome to Hatayaki Village!... That's what it says. Since
there are no tourists, no one will read it.

Here is a fun pig! Let's touch it and become happy with its
warmth!

I am growing corn for pig farming. Theft is a crime. You
should never do it. Don't you think it's pitiful to see cute
pigs go hungry?

It's as if... it resembles Lunaroa's flames... My health has
fully recovered!

\SE[16]Welcome. Laura. \SE[0]This is the world of Mama's
memories...

\SE[32]Throughout my life... the fun times, the difficult
times... \SE[3]This place is filled with so many memories...

\SE[14]W-Well, it's not like I came here to bother you or
anything...? \SE[43]I just thought that if Laura was alone,
she might get lost, so I wanted to go with her...

\SE[2]Didn't I tell you before? \.I have a lot of friends so
I don't feel lonely. \!\SE[0]You helped me the other day
too.

\SE\SE[2]But that child is different... \SE[3]She's all
alone. She depends on Mama. \SE\SE[2]She's much more of a
clingy person than me.

\SE[16]See? Let's move forward, okay? \SE[15]If we're
together, you won't feel lonely, right?

\SE[21]Right now, I'm really tired... Fighting or anything
like that, it seems impossible for me. \SE[5]If something
happens, will you protect me...?
